<item>
            <title>[LU-20091] Allow disabling MMP with failover configuration for cloud deployments</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-20091</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need a way to disable Multi-Mount Protection (MMP) on Lustre targets that have failover configuration (via &lt;tt&gt;-&lt;/tt&gt;servicenode or &lt;tt&gt;-failnode&lt;/tt&gt;). Currently, MMP is automatically enabled when failover is configured, with no option to override this behaviour.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
